import { Box, Grid, makeStyles,Typography,Divider } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'


const useStyles = makeStyles((theme)=>({
    root:{
        margin:20,
        padding:20,
        backgroundColor:'rgb(92.9%,92.9%,92.9%)'
    }

}))


const TodoContainer = () => {
    const classes = useStyles();

  return (
        <Box className={classes.root}>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
                <Grid item xs={8}>
                    <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom style={{textAlign:'left'}}>
                        Todo list
                    </Typography>
                    <Divider />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={4}>
                    <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom style={{textAlign:'left'}}>
                        completed
                    </Typography>
                    <Divider />
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Box>
  )
}

export default TodoContainer
